{"tid":486920,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"能仁書院學生算唔算瀕危物種？","createTime":"2017-12-02T09:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T12:16:26.000Z","uid":53062,"like":153,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"d6b90b73f60b87fda13dd3de9ae2ce06edc11de9","tid":486920,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"能仁學士學額80 只收6人<br />\n<br />\n17間開設學士學位課程的自資院校當中，最少13間實際收生人數低於學額。能仁專上學院本學年預計收生學額為80，實際收生卻只有6人。校長黃景波稱，收生人數較多的自資院校多是校舍及規模較大的，他承認收生不理想，期望明年學校能開設兩個新學科，吸引更多學生報讀。<br />\n<br />\n繼能仁十二門徒，今年有能仁六壯士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聯合國應該列能仁書院入文化遺產"},{"pid":"a0936fd9f7d15b68d566c438e7f26de06d1c809a","tid":486920,"uid":108236,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:16:19.000Z","msg":"撚仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044181a8e15c68770b0ac2ba59e1f4e862ae3938","tid":486920,"uid":62532,"like":128,"dislike":1,"score":127,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"能仁收生真係嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5f899275b2588872b6d73385322d4281d1e45f","tid":486920,"uid":43117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"去能仁探險先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7580550948470d844aef3af07d304472d578bca8","tid":486920,"uid":5077,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>能仁收生真係嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n能忍才是能人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984e5fd9cd9c5aa9504801581cf2addfae9db27b","tid":486920,"uid":37708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:22:07.000Z","msg":"勁過八奇"},{"pid":"d7c2a3c60568bca85b871529e4bebd12a9ee4b1a","tid":486920,"uid":3063,"lik